    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, people always say \"it gets better\" or \"find a purpose\" but that's just noise. there's no hidden meaning or some grand design. it's just chemistry and physics and then nothing. it feels so much more honest to just admit that everything is a void and there's no way out of it. it's just a hollow cycle.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
