      "content": "even those small things feel like a joke. a cup of tea or a walk doesn't change the fact that we're just cruising toward an inevitable end in a universe that doesn't care. it just feels like i'm dragging this heavy, pointless weight around for no reason. why bother trying to anchor myself to a reality that is fundamentally empty?",
